is to really look at
community living broadly.

00:29:47.354 --> 00:29:50.421
And transforming systems of care

00:29:50.421 --> 00:29:54.282
and the history of The
Lanterman Act really is about

00:29:54.282 --> 00:29:57.569
sort of transformation of
different kind of approach

00:29:57.569 --> 00:30:00.252
than the typical government
approach to services.

