of having a grooming goal

00:47:16.812 --> 00:47:18.347
and hammering on them.

00:47:18.347 --> 00:47:20.259
And what normal grooming
was we would take them

00:47:20.259 --> 00:47:22.647
to the hospital and say
if you wanna work here,

00:47:22.647 --> 00:47:25.052
you're gonna have to take a shower man.

00:47:25.052 --> 00:47:29.933
So that was huge change and I
think we're still undergoing

00:47:29.933 --> 00:47:32.959
