00:58:39.976 --> 00:58:41.882
of regional centers including Golden Gate

00:58:41.882 --> 00:58:44.456
to try to bring consultation to homes

00:58:44.456 --> 00:58:48.057
and training to homes around
particular individuals

00:58:48.057 --> 00:58:51.390
in nursing, in psychiatry and psychology

00:58:52.673 --> 00:58:57.109
and with parent sort of
family support experts.

00:58:57.109 --> 00:58:59.969
And we are really
looking forward to having

00:58:59.969 --> 00:59:02.724
that help expand our capacity

00:59:02.724 --> 00:59:06.057
and make our services of higher quality.

00:59:07.673 --> 00:59:09.702
I'll end just by referring back

00:59:09.702 --> 00:59:12.589
to Martin Luther King one more time.

00:59:12.589 --> 00:59:16.339
He says the arc of the
moral universe is long

00:59:18.355 --> 00:59:20.107
but it bends towards justice.

00:59:20.107 --> 00:59:22.529
So the fact that we are
a 50 year old system

00:59:22.529 --> 00:59:24.941
and we're still dealing with some issues

00:59:24.941 --> 00:59:26.179
shouldn't discourage us.

00:59:26.179 --> 00:59:29.641
There's plenty of evidence
of that these changes

00:59:29.641 --> 00:59:32.359
take decades and sometimes centuries

00:59:32.359 --> 00:59:34.119
and we're in it for the long haul

00:59:34.119 --> 00:59:35.386
so thank you very much.

00:59:35.386 --> 00:59:38.636
(audience applauding)

